Authors@R: person("Christian", "DÃ¼ben", email = "christian.dueben@uni-hamburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package computes shortest paths between places taking barriers or cost surfaces into account. Apart from relating locations on Earth, 
  spaths can also compute shortest paths more generally on spheres and planes.
